comments: Fultz (ORL) makes marginal contact to the hand of Morant (MEM) during the drive however Morant (MEM) is able to move through the contact along his desired path.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes a legal screening position in Brooks' (MEM) path and firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
Brooks (MEM) applies his forearm to Ross' (ORL) hip at the start of his upward shooting motion and affects his jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fultz (ORL) and absorbs contact.
Vucevic (ORL) makes incidental contact to the arm of Morant (MEM) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Carter-Williams (ORL) although incidental foot to foot contact occurs as Carter-Williams (ORL) moves over the pick.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (ORL) firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
Gordon (MEM) maintains a bent forearm to Brooks' (MEM) side during his drive and releases as Brooks (MEM) extends to towards the rim during his shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Carter-Williams (ORL) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Carter- Williams (ORL) establishes a legal position outside of the RA and absorbs the contact initiated by Morant (MEM) during his driving shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) makes marginal contact with Fultz (ORL) as he brings the ball up the floor.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brooks (MEM) and firms up on his left leg when contact occurs.
Fultz (ORL) makes contact to Jones' (MEM) arm during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) removes his hand from Ross' (ORL) hip as he moves through his upward shooting motion during his jump shot attempt.
Carter-Williams (ORL) makes marginal contact with Brooks (MEM) as he attempts to commit a take foul however, Brooks (MEM) is able to move through the contact.
Brooks (MEM) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Melton (MEM) briefly grasps the jersey of Vucevic (ORL) prior to the inbound.
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Augustin (ORL).
